<BaseLayout
  title="AI automatizacija za moderne poslovne timove"
  description="RoutineForge gradi AI telefonske agente, chatbotove i sisteme automatizacije koji pomažu preduzećima da štede vreme i ne propuštaju klijente."
  canonical={`${SITE_URL}/sr/`}
  lang="sr"
>
  <div id="top" class="flow-grid-bg min-h-screen">
    <Navbar />

    <main>
      <section class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] lg:px-8 lg:py-28">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-sky-600 shadow-sm"><span class="h-2 w-2 animate-pulse rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>AI automatizacija koja radi dok spavate</p>
          <h1 class="max-w-3xl text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">Prestanite da gubite potencijalne klijente van radnog vremena. Neka AI odgovori, kvalifikuje i isprati svaki upit — automatski.</h1>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">Pretvorite svaki poziv, poruku i upit u brzo i dosledno iskustvo za klijenta, dok se vaš tim fokusira na posao koji samo ljudi mogu da rade.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <Button href="#contact">Zakažite besplatnu konsultaciju</Button>
            <Button href="#services" variant="secondary">Pogledajte usluge</Button>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5 max-w-2xl rounded-2xl border border-sky-100 bg-white/80 p-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-sky-700">Šta se dešava na pozivu?</p>
            <div class="mt-3 grid gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600 sm:grid-cols-3"><p class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-100 text-[10px] font-bold text-sky-700">1</span>Mapiramo usko grlo</p><p class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-100 text-[10px] font-bold text-sky-700">2</span>Biramo prvi sistem</p><p class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sky-100 text-[10px] font-bold text-sky-700">3</span>Dobijate jasne sledeće korake</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-2 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>Odgovor na upite za nekoliko sekundi</span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-2 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>Direktno zakazivanje u kalendar</span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-2 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-500"></span>Preuzimanje od strane tima po potrebi</span>
          </div>
            <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-2 border-t border-slate-200 pt-5 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500"><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>Bez dugoročnih ugovora</span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>Puštanje u rad za 2–4 nedelje</span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span>14 dana garancije povraćaja novca</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-[0_30px_90px_-20px_rgba(15,23,42,0.25)] backdrop-blur-xl sm:p-8">
          <LiveDemoCard
            eyebrow="Tok rada uživo"
            title="Klijent → AI agent → CRM"
            badge="24/7 aktivno"
            messages={[
              { sender: 'customer', text: '„Želim da zakažem konsultaciju za petak.“' },
              { sender: 'ai', text: '„Imam par slobodnih termina — koje vreme vam odgovara?“' },
              { sender: 'customer', text: '„14h mi odgovara.“' },
              { sender: 'ai', text: '„Odlično, zakazano je za petak u 14h.“' }
            ]}
            statusLabel="Ažuriranje sistema"
